name: o_god_the_mail_13
description:
These ads I get and get and get - am I expected to look at them? So much time and money sending this paper around the world to people who don't want to look at it and are forced to move it from their box or their life-changing papers might get blocked. As long as I'm alive I have to deal with these. All these faces that come on glossy printed cardstock trying to get me to buy a membership or a drug or some new car or something. I can't ignore them either - o god, the mail.

"The paper holds their folded faces to the floor
And every day the paper boy brings more."
